{"tid":2166562,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄧炳強被制裁 警察乘勢打擊元朗黑勢力?","createTime":"2020-08-20T13:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T01:13:57.000Z","uid":185631,"like":29,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"5b13c5e30f6b73fca19132716ba8b41473f27a63","tid":2166562,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"<strong>跨部門打擊元朗區黑社會活動 325男女被捕</strong><br />\n<br />\n警方鑑於元朗區涉及黑社會嚴重案件有上升趨勢，經情報分析及深入調查，元朗警區刑事部、特別職務隊聯同海關及消防處，於11日起一連9日採取「勇進」行動，在元朗、天水圍及八鄉，搗破兩個色情場所、11個非法賭檔、一個釣魚機場、兩個毒品派對場所、三間無牌酒吧及三個非法油站。<br />\n<br />\n警方在行動中拘捕157男168女，年齡由17至82歲，當中11人有黑社會背景。檢獲總值約52萬元物品，包括毒品、賭款、麻將、麻將枱、啤牌、釣魚機、未完稅香煙、未完稅汽油及柴油等。警方相信行動已成功打擊黑社會活動及其收入來源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200820/s00001/1597917203069/%E8%B7%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E5%8D%80%E9%BB%91%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-325%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200820%2Fs00001%2F1597917203069%2F%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%25BB%2591%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-325%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5SrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=0af4839d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200820%2Fs00001%2F1597917203069%2F%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%25BB%2591%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-325%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595&h=b6f4ebda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200820/s00001/1597917203069/%E8